# AI Citation Optimizer — agent navigation

**Start here:** read `docs/AGENT_CONTEXT.md` for the file map, API contracts, and known bugs. Do not explore the whole repo — open only the files listed there.

## Stack

| Layer | Path | Tooling |
|-------|------|---------|
| API | `backend/app/` | FastAPI, Python 3.12, Playwright 1.48, LangChain + Gemini |
| UI | `frontend/src/` | React 19, Vite, Tailwind, **pnpm** |
| Infra | `docker-compose.yml` | backend :8000, frontend :5173 |

## Where to edit (common tasks)

- New/changed endpoint → `backend/app/main.py`
- Playwright audit / fix guidance → `backend/app/agent.py`
- llms.txt probe/template → `backend/app/llms_txt_analyzer.py`
- Sitemap gaps → `backend/app/sitemap_analyzer.py`
- Peec API → `backend/app/peec_client.py`
- Dashboard / fix panel → `frontend/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx`
- Deep audit page → `frontend/src/pages/PageDetail.jsx`

## Dev commands (local — any OS)

```bash
npm run setup   # first time: install Python + pnpm deps
npm run dev     # start backend + frontend together

# Docker (macOS / Windows / WSL)
npm run docker:up
```

Env: `PEEC_API_KEY`, `GEMINI_API_KEY` in root `.env`.

